Module backend.domain.main
Package de.eatological.domain

Record Class Ingredient

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
de.eatological.domain.Ingredient
Record Components:
name - String, the name of the ingredient
unit - String, the unit for this ingredient
smallestAmount - float, the smallest amount of "unit" in which this ingredient can be used
localTimeFrame - LocalTimeFrame the timeframe of the local availability
co2 - float, amount of produced co2 per smallest amount of ingredient
alternativeText - String, some text which describes alternatives for this ingredient
public record Ingredient(int id, String name, String unit, float smallestAmount, @Nullable LocalTimeFrame localTimeFrame, float co2, @Nullable String alternativeText) extends Record
Represents a single ingredient.
